{"tid":2084334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個friend撞咗我架車 然後佢屌鳩我","createTime":"2020-06-29T07:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:06:13.000Z","uid":200974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b12f24f7e931295f26eb55a44f8f5d477e4b25fd","tid":2084334,"uid":200974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日借咗架車俾個friend去型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知揸咗一個鐘都冇 佢就打電話俾我話撞咗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我當然第一時間去睇睇<br />\n一睇 哇屌 個泵把變撚左型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我梗係即刻屌鳩佢 <br />\n本身諗住屌佢兩句 佢扮下死狗就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知當我屌到兩句之後 佢一鳩屌埋你同我講<br />\n泵把就係要來撞㗎啦 唔撞攞嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻呆撚咗 但又駁唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後佢頭也不回就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集思廣益 我應該點樣駁返佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e342388153924d91315f309d23c754dc387cbf36","tid":2084334,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"問候佢伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2acc078ae0c69e3e92914eef27244631d55dcc3","tid":2084334,"uid":230416,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BumevxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBumevxA.jpg&h=90d749ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7191dcb62287c270fa10382be8a9818385dc39b5","tid":2084334,"uid":71913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyT